queries.sql: SELECT `sk`.`id_satker`, `sk`.`thn_anggaran`, `stkr`.`nama_satker`, `stkr`.`pembina`, COALESCE(spm.status, 0) AS status_pim, COALESCE(spk.status, 0) AS status_kpk, COALESCE(slvl.status, 0) AS status_klvl FROM `sk_pmsatker` AS `sk` LEFT JOIN `satker` AS `stkr` ON `stkr`.`id` = `sk`.`id_satker` LEFT JOIN `status_pim` AS `spm` ON `spm`.`id_satker` = `sk`.`id_satker` AND `spm`.`thn_dipa` = `sk`.`thn_anggaran` LEFT JOIN `status_kpk` AS `spk` ON `spk`.`id_satker` = `sk`.`id_satker` AND `spk`.`thn_dipa` = `sk`.`thn_anggaran` LEFT JOIN `status_klvl` AS `slvl` ON `slvl`.`id_satker` = `sk`.`id_satker` AND `slvl`.`thn_dipa` = `sk`.`thn_anggaran` ORDER BY `sk`.`thn_anggaran` DESC
